  stimulus_text = 'A recent study by the American Medical Association found that many patients are hesitant to use telemedicine, or remote medical care, because of concerns about privacy and the quality of care.  However, patients who have used telemedicine reported higher satisfaction rates and more positive experiences than those who have not. What is the most likely reason why the writer uses the word "however"?',
